title: BRIEF-Kerlink Supports Expansion Of Senet's Low Power Wide Area Network In Las Vegas‍​

organizations.name: low power wide area network in las vegas‍​ jan

text:
Jan 8 (Reuters) - KERLINK SA:
* SUPPORTS EXPANSION OF SENET’S LOW POWER WIDE AREA NETWORK IN LAS VEGAS‍​
* COLLABORATIVE EXPANSION OF SENET’S GLOBAL LOW POWER WIDE AREA NETWORK (LPWA) IN LAS VEGAS AREA
* EXPANSION TO SUPPORT VARIETY OF COMMERCIAL SOLUTION OFFERINGS, MARKET TRIALS AND PROOFS OF CONCEPT Source text: bit.ly/2meFLR4 Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
